===more:The Visalia photographs stand in stark contrast to the earlier pictures taken by Lange and Rothstein of migrant laborers and of the impact of the dust storms. Create two contrasting pairs of images. Explain what an analysis of each pair tells us about the experience of the Great Depression.  
